Package co.cask.cdap.api.procedure Description

Procedure implementations.

Every procedure should implement the Procedure interface. For convenience the package comes with AbstractProcedure class which implements basic initialization logic that is preferable to use in most cases.

Deprecated as of version 2.6.0, with no direct replacement, see Service
